metadata.name: AQUA-E01 "Confidence"
metadata.description:
AQUA-E displaying the emotion: Confidence.

The first in the AI Emotions series.

AI Emotions is a collection of anime-inspired digital paintings made from both hand and AI, featuring several characters with varying expressions.

Each artwork has been created using a combination of digital painting by hand using Photoshop and a digital art tablet, alongside various Artificial Intelligence art programs.

Thanks for viewing :)
